    <thetext>Build ID: 3.2

Steps To Reproduce:
1. Turn off auto build
2. Modify a file in a project but don&apos;t save
3. Use Project&gt;Build to build the project
- Note that you are not prompted to save the changed artifact

This is a usability problem as the user may not notice that
the change has not been saved and will not be running with the change.


More information:</thetext>
